snippet.textDisplay:
First we got Princess Catgirl by Cashmere Cat, then [USA] by Anamanaguchi, and then Good Faith by Madeon. Finally, Porter has returned, too! This has been an amazing past few months for this specific flavor of EDM. This song sounds so fresh, yet so familiar. There's definitely a lot more organic sounds here--the lo-fi piano, the acoustic drum samples--, but also a lot of the synthetic, video game-like sounds Porter is known for, and they blend together perfectly. I'm ready for whatever is in store for us with Nurture.
If you like this song, you should definitely check out the other three artists I listed, as they have a similar vibe. Porter even co-wrote some of the songs on [USA].
